<dl id="n12230f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12230f">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12230f"> 230(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> to wear the White Shirt</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Jasto, now, my little father Simon has gone <mark>to wear the White Shirt</mark> in the Palace <font color="green">[has died]</font>. Come you then and carry him on your shoulders nice into Sion. <small> Caradoc Evans, <a name="EVAN" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#EVAN"><cite title="source">My People</cite></a> (1915) 40-41 [The Way of the Earth]</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
